divs: Sighting DetailsI was flying my plane one night it was about 230 a.m. My dog was acting kind ofstrange, he was barking out the window. So i grabbed my bottle of whiskey andthrew it at him it was empty anyways. Then i started to feel tingly inside. So ifigured i should land so I could use the restroom. All of a sudden I felt verywarm and off into a distance i saw something strange. I started to get extremelydizzy. Then I felt like I was sick I saw ten of those things i wished I hadsomeone with me to experience what i saw. I was completely amazed after it wasover I couldnt believe something like that was going on. It was flaming acrossthe sky then it started shooting out laser beams and started to shoot at me so igot out my other bottle of whiskey out cause i just didnt know what else to do.I asked my injured dog if he had seen it too and he said gimme another drink andmaybe I will. Then I woke up in this strange place and after I opened my eyesand I saw the strange place and saw many strange things it looked like aliens.All the while my dog was completely ambiguous to what was going on.
